        %hr.section-heading-spacer
        %p.clear-left
          Deliver CSS/SCSS architecture / Hand-off
        %p.clear-left.section-body-text
          Having the lead developer involved during the final user testing review, gave him a clear understanding of what we were trying to accomplish with this product. We had established an open dialog between him and the call center lead, so he could quickly solve basic interaction roadblocks and keep us within the project's timeline. Having the design patterns scoped during the previous phase streamlined the development cycle and lead to less brittle code.
